      "content": "i know, i know, but i'm literally just sitting in my hotel room and i don't want to go to an emergency room in a different country if i don't have to. it's probably just the cabin pressure and some anxiety from the delay, right? i feel like i'm just hyperventilating a bit. can't i just try some deep breathing exercises or maybe take a sedative to calm down and see if it passes?",
